description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Express Bodyweight Strength' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The The Disciplined Grind vibe means No excuses, no distractions, just execute. This is especially good for When you want pure focus and efficiency..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Get in an efficient workout with Pete during this quick circuit of three bodyweight exercises. ...
